


WN10-AU-000500 - pass

The Application event log size must be configured to 32768 KB or greater.

Steps
1. Tenable Discovered STIGS FAILURE

WN10-AU-000500

\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\EventLog\Application\

Registry Hive: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE
Registry Path: \SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\EventLog\Application\

Value Name: MaxSize

Value Type: REG_DWORD
Value: 0x00008000 (32768) (or greater)

2. Followed advice given from Tenanble in the Check cololum
3. Found that EventLog\Application and value Maxsize doesn't exist
4. Created the following pathway manually and value to log size
 	-- Right click on Windows > New > Key > EventLog
 	- Right click on EventLog > New > Key > Application
 	- - Right click on Application > New > DWORD > Name it MaxSize
 	- Right click Maxsize  > Modify - Set hex value to 8000 and decimal to 32768
5. Restarted computer
6. Run Tenable and WN10-AU-000500 passed

Code Below:

# Define registry path and desired value
$regPath = "HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\EventLog\Application\"


Set-ItemProperty -Path $regPath -Name "MaxSize" -Value 32768 -Type DWord


